name: Meet Awesome Makers - Eric Wilhelm, Founder of Instructables
description: Every true blooded Maker needs no introduction to the awesome project sharing site that is Instructables. We are beyond honoured to have the founder Eric Wilhelm spend his evening with Singapore Makers at the Prototyping Lab@National Design Centre.
location: Prototyping Lab @ NDC, 111 Middle Road, National Design Centre, #01-02 Singapore
